---
import Icon from "astro-icon";
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-3" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Hi, I'm Musa, a front-end software developer from Turkey.
      <br />
       My primary tools of choice includes:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>HTML</li>
        <li>CSS</li>
        <li>JavaScript</li>
        <li>React.js</li>
        <li>Redux Toolkit</li>
        <li>Material UI</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about hypercars and financial literacy.
      An unusual hobby of mine is collecting wet wipes, they're
      interesting pieces of restaurants.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each project.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
